OL,3,CTwo Isle of Wight primary schools to
OL,4,Cclose this summer
OL,6,FTwo primary schools on the Isle of
OL,7,FWight will be forced to close this
OL,8,Fsummer following a council meeting.
OL,10,FThe decision to shut Cowes Primary
OL,11,FSchool and Arreton St George's CE
OL,12,FPrimary School was made by the Isle of
OL,13,FWight Council's cabinet on Thursday
OL,14,Fnight.
OL,16,FThe authority says the closures are a
OL,17,Fresponse to a surplus of school places
OL,18,Fon the island, due to declining pupil
OL,19,Fnumbers, which it says have been
OL,20,Fnegatively impacting education
OL,21,Fstandards.
