OL,3,CTwo Isle of Wight primary schools to
OL,4,Cclose this summer
OL,6,FThree primary schools - Oakfield and
OL,7,FBrading CofE Primary Schools, and
OL,8,FWroxall Primary School - have been
OL,9,Fsaved after their proposed closure was
OL,10,Frejected by the Cabinet.
OL,12,FIt follows months of protests against
OL,13,Fthe proposals by parents, concerned
OL,14,Ftheir children will be disadvantaged.
OL,16,FIn a statement, the Diocese of
OL,17,FPortsmouth said: "We remain concerned
OL,18,Fregarding the process that led to the
OL,19,Fdecision to close Arreton St George's
OL,20,FCofE Primary School and Cowes Primary
OL,21,FSchool.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
