OL,3,CTwo Isle of Wight primary schools to
OL,4,Cclose this summer
OL,6,F"We are therefore taking legal advice
OL,7,Fand will continue to consider all
OL,8,Foptions as advised.
OL,10,F"We are pleased that the proposed
OL,11,Fclosure of Oakfield and Brading CofE
OL,12,FPrimary Schools, and Wroxall Primary
OL,13,FSchool have been rejected by the
OL,14,FCabinet."
OL,16,FThe council has appointed a dedicated
OL,17,Fofficer to assist pupils and staff
OL,18,Fduring the transition.
