OL,3,CTwo Isle of Wight primary schools to
OL,4,Cclose this summer
OL,6,FThe officer will coordinate support
OL,7,Fservices, liaise with affected
OL,8,Fschools, and ensure that the
OL,9,Ftransition "is as smooth as possible"
OL,10,Ffor all involved.
OL,12,FThe council says it will provide
OL,13,Ftailored transition plans for some
OL,14,Fstudents to help them to adapt to
OL,15,Ftheir new school environment.
OL,17,FOther measures due to be introduced
OL,18,Finclude support groups and buddy
OL,19,Fsystems.
