OL,3,CTwo Isle of Wight primary schools to
OL,4,Cclose this summer
OL,6,FThe authority says it will try to
OL,7,Fredeploy staff to other schools on the
OL,8,Fisland, to help ensure job security
OL,9,Fand continuity. Training and
OL,10,Fcounselling will also be offered to
OL,11,Faffected staff members.
OL,13,FCouncillor Phil Jordan, council
OL,14,Fleader, said: "We understand that this
OL,15,Ftransition may be challenging for some
OL,16,Ffamilies, but we are committed to
OL,17,Fsupporting our pupils and staff every
OL,18,Fstep of the way.
